{"tid":1102897,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[世界紀錄] 賓州消防員負50磅跑半馬","createTime":"2019-04-12T04:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T11:00:25.000Z","uid":28366,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2d4d031b47a8d775e11fd4f58205dc9c4633eb","tid":1102897,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/%E8%B3%93%E5%B7%9E%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A1%E8%B2%A050%E7%A3%85%E8%B7%91%E5%8D%8A%E9%A6%AC-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F%25E8%25B3%2593%25E5%25B7%259E%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B2%25A050%25E7%25A3%2585%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%258D%258A%25E9%25A6%25AC-1.jpg&h=1893c31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自美國賓夕凡尼亞州嘅消防員 Ryan，早前參加當地嘅半馬賽事。不過佢絕對唔係輕裝上陣，而係 full gear，孭晒成套救火裝備上身，希望可以完成半馬賽事，亦希望可以將呢項創舉收錄於《健力士紀錄大全》。<br />\n<br />\n場比賽都係一般嘅長跑比賽，無乜好講。反而值得介紹 Ryan 身上嘅裝備。佢著齊晒入火場嘅防火衣、防火褲，腳上穿上長 boot，頭戴鋼盔，仲孭住一罐氧氣，以及呼吸器 (SCBA) 跑步。呢堆裝備，一共重50磅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/%E8%B3%93%E5%B7%9E%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A1%E8%B2%A050%E7%A3%85%E8%B7%91%E5%8D%8A%E9%A6%AC-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F%25E8%25B3%2593%25E5%25B7%259E%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B2%25A050%25E7%25A3%2585%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%258D%258A%25E9%25A6%25AC-2.jpg&h=961cc4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而佢咁辛苦比賽嘅目的，係希望可以令民眾更加明白消防員日常工作嘅辛苦，以及記念已去世嘅消防隊長爸爸。<br />\n<br />\n呢次佢亦聯絡咗《健力士紀錄大全》，希望可以將成績收錄喺裏面。有關方面定下3小時30分嘅門檻。可惜，Ryan 末段力竭，只能以3小時36分完賽，未能成為世界紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/%E8%B3%93%E5%B7%9E%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A1%E8%B2%A050%E7%A3%85%E8%B7%91%E5%8D%8A%E9%A6%AC-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F%25E8%25B3%2593%25E5%25B7%259E%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B2%25A050%25E7%25A3%2585%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%258D%258A%25E9%25A6%25AC-3.jpg&h=5ab6c460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢呢次就籌到5,800美金嘅善款，用以幫助患病嘅消防員。<br />\n<br />\n講開又講，今年一月嘅廈門馬拉松，內地消防員徐佚豪孭住20磅以3小時40分完成全馬。不過事後被發現佢用咗人哋嘅號碼布出賽。結果被當判終身停賽，不得再參加廈門馬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fitz.hk/sports/running/挑戰世界紀錄-賓州消防員負50磅跑半馬/?fbclid=IwAR0oN6e_Bg14jlYrx7ai2c48uJ2e8tL-FQbsrgTqMQu6hRegdjzQQlljmZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Fsports%2Frunning%2F%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E8%B3%93%E5%B7%9E%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A1%E8%B2%A050%E7%A3%85%E8%B7%91%E5%8D%8A%E9%A6%AC%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0oN6e_Bg14jlYrx7ai2c48uJ2e8tL-FQbsrgTqMQu6hRegdjzQQlljmZA&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzlR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=a1318ffa\" target=\"_blank\">https://fitz.hk/sports/running/挑戰世界紀錄-賓州消防員負50磅跑半馬/?fbclid=IwAR0oN6e_Bg14jlYrx7ai2c48uJ2e8tL-FQbsrgTqMQu6hRegdjzQQlljmZA</a>"},{"pid":"ec69c2d079e795c0251ebcf71038a9702bebed2a","tid":1102897,"uid":2373,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:01:59.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗消防員賓州負50磅跑半馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c83187b4f4f4b1c19ca865691a5ca0d4d3893c","tid":1102897,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e239c80facab8c818235e3290672298c0ac8cec5","tid":1102897,"uid":164770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"熱都熱都顛"},{"pid":"7d480cca429ba2d44d39f22c8bf3bbdb3d374b26","tid":1102897,"uid":121040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"奥巴馬搖擺賓洲"},{"pid":"c809dc7ef892d68fb8c2341a8730fff67c5184e9","tid":1102897,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"講開又講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\